WEBVTT

00:02.127 --> 00:03.311
Kids, have I ever told you

00:03.313 --> 00:05.596
the story
of how I met your father?

00:05.598 --> 00:06.897
Well, I'll just skip ahead

00:06.899 --> 00:09.433
to the moment I told him
I was pregnant.

00:10.936 --> 00:13.187
W... What happened?

00:13.189 --> 00:14.488
Did I pass out?

00:14.490 --> 00:16.274
Not exactly.

00:16.276 --> 00:18.409
I'm pregnant.

00:21.663 --> 00:24.448
Are you sure you're not
just getting fat?

00:26.451 --> 00:28.919
Oh, yeah.

00:28.921 --> 00:31.339
So, um, you're pregnant.

00:31.341 --> 00:32.372
Yeah.

00:32.375 --> 00:34.175
Huh.

00:34.177 --> 00:36.544
Looks like nobody told
your boobs.

00:38.680 --> 00:41.332
What happened?

00:41.334 --> 00:42.633
Did I pass out?

00:42.635 --> 00:43.384
Oh, my...

00:43.386 --> 00:44.501
Please stop hitting me!

00:44.503 --> 00:46.771
Hey.

00:46.773 --> 00:51.058
Are... Are you sure you're...

00:51.060 --> 00:52.977
Well, no, not positive.

00:52.979 --> 00:54.395
I'm a week late.

00:54.397 --> 00:56.614
But I'm never late;
it's a point of pride with me.

00:56.616 --> 00:57.681
I'm going to go

00:57.683 --> 00:59.867
see the doctor on Monday
to find out for sure.

00:59.869 --> 01:03.070
Until then, not a word
of this to anyone.

01:03.072 --> 01:04.288
Not even Kevin?

01:05.022 --> 01:07.958
I mean, it's probably his.

01:07.960 --> 01:09.827
I've spent years
training my boys

01:09.829 --> 01:11.212
to swim the other way.

01:11.214 --> 01:13.164
Kevin and I haven't had sex yet.

01:14.066 --> 01:16.533
If I'm pregnant, you're the dad.

01:18.387 --> 01:20.537
That's wonderful!

01:20.539 --> 01:21.722
Huh?

01:21.724 --> 01:23.674
I'm gonna be a daddy!

