01:45.598 --> 01:46.547
Stop it.

01:46.549 --> 01:47.548
Sorry, sorry.

01:47.550 --> 01:48.599
Keeping it secret.

01:49.752 --> 01:52.253
Oop, I think I gave you
the wrong one.

01:52.255 --> 01:53.437
Here, let me just...

01:53.439 --> 01:55.389
Give it to me.
Drop... let go.

01:55.391 --> 01:58.726
Take it away from you.

01:59.611 --> 02:01.946
Barney, why are you
so happy about this?

02:01.948 --> 02:02.947
Because this is perfect.

02:02.949 --> 02:04.315
