will I ever want kids.

02:17.380 --> 02:20.047
Sorry, kids.

02:20.049 --> 02:22.383
I can't have a baby.

02:22.385 --> 02:23.467
Hey, guys!

02:23.469 --> 02:27.054
Guess what this is!

02:27.056 --> 02:29.290
One of your socks?
Boom! You're huge.

02:29.292 --> 02:32.459
No, it's our unborn son's
Christmas stocking.

02:32.461 --> 02:34.011
Grandma Gunderson
started knitting it

02:34.013 --> 02:36.397
the day Lily and I got married.

02:36.399 --> 02:40.401
