for our shower.

03:03.042 --> 03:04.325
No can do.

03:04.327 --> 03:08.429
Um, I have a big project
that I'm working on.

03:08.431 --> 03:12.383
This is Richard Holdman's house
in East Meadow.

03:12.385 --> 03:15.636
Last year, he had the
most visited Christmas display

03:15.638 --> 03:16.887
