04:44.142 --> 04:47.094
Insane Duane?

04:48.997 --> 04:50.531
Barney?

04:50.533 --> 04:53.284
<i>Insane Duane was your father's</i>
<i>best friend,</i>

04:53.286 --> 04:56.537
<i>back in the days before</i>
<i>he met me or your Uncle Ted.</i>

04:58.407 --> 04:59.907
We're going back to her place.

04:59.909 --> 05:00.908
Boom!

05:00.910 --> 05:02.410
All right, you win!

05:02.412 --> 05:04.778
Here's 20 for picking up a girl
with only one word.

05:04.780 --> 05:06.780
