for that word being "boner."

05:06.782 --> 05:08.416
Thank you.

05:08.418 --> 05:13.120
I'll meet you back here in an
hour when I'm done with, uh...

05:14.122 --> 05:15.556
Ah, who cares what her name is;
she won't be

05:15.558 --> 05:16.640
