preschools and poops.

05:34.243 --> 05:36.160
I haven't set foot
in a bar in years.

05:36.162 --> 05:37.828
You stopped drinking?

05:37.830 --> 05:40.781
Oh, I still drink.

05:42.284 --> 05:44.168
Vaginal
numbing spray.

05:44.170 --> 05:45.753
Apparently, after child birth,

05:45.755 --> 05:48.372
your hoo-ha looks like
Rocky Balboa's face.

05:48.374 --> 05:51.425
- You can't have a baby!
- I can't have a baby!

05:52.360 --> 05:54.995
<i>The next day,</i>
<i>we went to the doctor.</i>

05:54.997 --> 05:56.347
Well, Mrs. Scherbatsky,

05:56.349 --> 05:58.332
I'm sure that you
and your husband...

05:58.334 --> 05:59.767
Uh, he's not my husband.

05:59.769 --> 06:00.718
Oh, I'm so sorry.

06:00.720 --> 06:01.835
