06:12.281 --> 06:14.615
Um, you: not pregnant.

06:14.617 --> 06:16.183
Yeah!

06:16.185 --> 06:17.568
- Oh, yeah!
- Yeah!

06:17.570 --> 06:19.520
That's what I'm
talking about!

06:22.875 --> 06:24.708
Yeah, you know,
you know!

06:24.710 --> 06:27.194
