to someone...

08:10.484 --> 08:14.236
Robin, is there anyone
you can talk to about this?

08:14.238 --> 08:15.871
Perhaps a close friend?

08:15.873 --> 08:18.206
<i>I knew I could have</i>
<i>talked to my friends.</i>

08:18.208 --> 08:20.041
<i>But, it's just, I already knew</i>

08:20.043 --> 08:22.127
<i>exactly how</i>
<i>they would all react.</i>

08:22.129 --> 08:25.163
<i>Ted would go into overdrive</i>
<i>trying to make me feel better.</i>

08:25.165 --> 08:26.548
