on and on about babies.

08:45.802 --> 08:50.071
Oh, I am such a bad friend!

08:51.741 --> 08:53.775
<i>And I'd wind up comforting her.</i>

08:53.777 --> 08:54.743
It's okay.

08:54.745 --> 08:57.645
You have to punch
me in the face!

08:57.647 --> 08:59.948
<i>Marshall would ask me</i>
<i>a ton of questions</i>

08:59.950 --> 09:01.499
<i>I don't know the answers to.</i>

09:01.501 --> 09:03.652
- Have you thought about adoption?
- Um, well...

09:03.654 --> 09:05.337
Does this kind of thing
run in your family?

09:05.339 --> 09:06.171
Uh...

09:06.173 --> 09:07.205
What was the date, duration

09:07.207 --> 09:10.008
and consistency
of your last period?

09:10.010 --> 09:12.627
<i>And your father would</i>
<i>bend over backwards</i>

09:12.629 --> 09:14.095
<i>trying to make me laugh.</i>

09:14.097 --> 09:16.497
A priest and a rabbi
walk into a bar--

09:16.499 --> 09:18.850
no, a barbershop--
no, a post office--

09:18.852 --> 09:21.386
no, it's two priests--
no, it's two ducks--

09:21.388 --> 09:23.671
