could be Polish, too.

09:26.643 --> 09:27.859
Doesn't matter.

09:27.861 --> 09:29.694
Yes it does.
The duck's not Polish.

09:29.696 --> 09:30.779
<i>And when that didn't work,</i>

09:30.781 --> 09:32.948
