<i>bend over backwards.</i>

09:32.950 --> 09:34.583
Pratfall!

09:34.585 --> 09:36.134
Ow!

09:36.136 --> 09:39.520
<i>The bottom line is, I didn't</i>
<i>feel like talking about it.</i>

09:39.522 --> 09:41.656
